\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Piker Alpha's {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/Piker-Alpha/ssdtPRGen.sh"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 ssdtPRGen}} script will generate a SSDT you can use to achieve the maximum amount of power states for your desktop CPU. Please note that desktop power management is not mandatory.\
